{"title":"人民日报发行情况读者调查问卷","authors":[],"dates":[{"year":1994,"month":6,"day":15}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"人民日报发行情况读者调查问卷"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"亲爱的读者："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"今天是人民日报创刊４６周年纪念日，迄今本报已出版１６７７６期。为了广泛听取读者意见，进一步办好人民日报，我们决定进行一次规模较大的读者问卷调查。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这次刊出的问卷题目侧重于了解本报读者构成、订阅与阅读、发行时效与印刷质量等基本情况，借此机会征求对本报发行工作的建议，目的是更好地为读者服务。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们热诚期望本报的公费、自费读者积极参与这次调查活动。在统计、分析工作结束后，我们将在公证部门的监督下，抽出“热心读者”４０名，纪念奖若干名，并在本报予以公布，９月中旬在北京召开颁奖大会。届时欢迎幸运读者到人民日报社参观、座谈，出席颁奖大会。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"此次问卷调查活动得到了太原高氏劳瑞油墨化学有限公司，上海市锦江（集团）公司，中共淄博市委、淄博市人民政府，山东鲁南化学工业（集团）公司，沈阳飞龙医药保健品集团，吉林纸业股份有限公司等单位的大力支持，谨表感谢。本次问卷答案回寄时间截至１９９４年７月１５日（以当地邮戳为准），请在信封正面贴上本次问卷调查徽志，贴足邮资，寄北京朝阳门外金台西路２号人民日报发行处。邮政编码：１００７３３；电话：５０９１５１６、５０２４５１６；传真：５０９１７１６。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"姓名："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"地址："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"邮政编码："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一、您的基本情况："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"Ａ．性别："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"１．男"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"２．女"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"Ｂ．年龄：　　１．２２岁以下"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"２．２３—３４岁"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"３．３５—４５岁"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"４．４６—６０岁"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"５．６１岁以上"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"Ｃ．职业："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"１．工人"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"２．农民"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"３．军人"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"４．党政干部"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"５．教科文卫工作者"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"６．企业管理人员"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"７．学生"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"８．个体经营者、劳动者"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"９．离、退休人员"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"１０．其他"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"Ｄ．单位、部门或组织：　　１．中国共产党的组织　　２．各级国家、政府机关"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"３．军事组织　　４．民主党派、人民团体"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"５．行政村"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"６．街道居民委员会"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"７．大专院校"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"８．中学（中专、中技等）、小学"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"９．文化、艺术、体育部门"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"１０．新闻、出版部门"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"１１．卫生、科研部门　　１２．国有企业　　１３．集体（乡镇）企业"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"１４．私营企业"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"１５．“三资”企业"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"１６．其他"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"Ｅ．级别："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"１．普通工作人员　　２．科级"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"３．处级"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"４．司局级以上"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"Ｆ．职称"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"１．初级职称"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"２．中级职称"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"３．高级职称"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"４．无"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"Ｇ．文化程度："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"１．初中以下"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"２．高中"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"３．大专以上"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"二、您阅读的人民日报来自："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"１．公费订阅"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"２．自费订阅"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"３．赠报"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"三、您经常在哪些地点阅读人民日报："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"１．办公室"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"２．图书馆、阅览室"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"３．阅报栏"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"４．家中"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"５．其他"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"四、您所阅读的人民日报通常有几人阅读："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"１．１人"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"２．２人"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"３．３—５人"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"４．６人以上"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"五、您阅读人民日报的历史："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"１．１—５年"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"２．６—１５年"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"３．１６—２５年"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"４．２６—４６年"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"六、您订阅人民日报主要目的是："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"１．了解党和国家的方针、政策"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"２．获取国内外信息"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"３．作为资料保存"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"七、一般情况下，您阅读时："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"１．仔细阅读每块版"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"２．阅读感兴趣的版面"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"３．只看标题"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"八、您所在地阅报栏中的人民日报："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"１．每日更换"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"２．偶尔更换"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"３．未贴"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"九、您对本报１９９５年将扩至十二版有何期望？（多选题）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"１．继续发挥人民日报的社论、评论和理论文章的优势"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"２．在保持高格调的同时，增加贴近群众的内容"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"３．加强当前热点问题的报道"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"４．增加地方新闻"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"十、一般情况下，您收到或看到人民日报的时间（以出版日期为准）："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"１．当天上午"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"２．当天下午"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"３．第２天"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"４．第３天以上"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"十一、您收到人民日报的时间与当地省级机关报相比："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"１．同时"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"２．晚"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"十二、您收到１９９４年每周二、五增出的人民日报九至十二版情况："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"１．同步"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"２．不同步"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"３．偶有短缺"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"４．经常短缺"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"十三、您认为人民日报的印刷质量："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"１．较好"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"２．一般"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"３．较差"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"十四、如果印刷质量较差，主要是："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"１．重影"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"２．字体不清"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"３．图片模糊"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"４．褶皱"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"十五、您认为提高人民日报发行量最重要的措施是：　　１．改进报纸内容"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"２．稳定或降低报价"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"３．加快发行时效"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"４．提高投递质量"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"５．提高印刷质量"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"十六、您认为人民日报目前的报纸定价："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"１．正常"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"２．偏高　　３．较低"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"十七、请您围绕以下几个方面对人民日报的内容进行评价："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"很好较好一般较差很差"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"１．权威性"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"２．可读性"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"３．时效性"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"十八、您最喜欢的本报版面是："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"１．要闻版"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"２．经济版"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"３．政法版"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"４．教科文卫版"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"５．理论版"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"６．文艺版"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"７．国际版"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"８．读者来信版"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"十九、您认为应如何改进人民日报的发行工作（具体建议请另附纸）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"填答问卷要求：凡未特别注明者外，每个问题只选一个答案；在您选中的答案的题号上划“√”；如所阅读的报纸需要保存，问卷可以复制。"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":5,"page_end":5}